Company Overview of Spire Capital Partners, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Spire Capital Partners, L.P. specializes in buyouts and growth capital investments. It seeks to invest in the commercial and professional services, media, communications equipment, and telecommunication services sectors. The fund typically invests in companies based in the United States of America. It prefers to invest between $15 million and $25 million in its portfolio companies.


1500 BroadwaySuite 1811New York, NY 10036United StatesFounded in 2000



Phone: 212-218-5454

Fax: 212-218-5455








