Piper D. Leonard

















Piper D. Leonard
Director of Finance

 




























Piper joined Spire Capital in April 2013 as Director of Finance. Piper works alongside the CFO on internal accounting, control and compliance matters as well as working with portfolio company investments on financial and operational issues. Prior to joining Spire, Piper served as CFO at Ariston Global, a portfolio company of Spire. At Ariston, Piper was responsible for all aspects of the company’s accounting and finance operations.
Prior to joining Ariston, Piper was the Area Controller for Loomis Armored US Inc. responsible for  financial management functions in the southwest region. Prior to Loomis, Piper worked for PricewaterhouseCoopers in the Audit and Assurance division where she focused primarily on the telecommunication industry.  She received a Master of Business Administration degree from the University of Central Arkansas and a Bachelor of Science in Accounting at University of Arkansas at Little Rock.










